公众对格雷之死的反应，与2014年[[迈克尔·布朗枪击案|迈克尔·布朗枪击案]]相似，美国警察动用武力，尤其是向非裔美国人成为争议的焦点<ref name=bbc-dualidentity>{{cite web|last1=Swift|first1=Tim|title=Baltimore's dual identity explains unrest|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-32499923|website=BBC News|accessdate=2015-04-28|archive-date=2022-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220102095754/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-32499923}}</ref><ref name=nyt-natguard>{{cite news|last1=Stolberg|first1=Sheryl Gay|title=Baltimore Enlists National Guard and a Curfew to Fight Riots and Looting|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/28/us/baltimore-freddie-gray.html|accessdate=2015-04-28|work=The New York Times|date=2015-04-27|archive-date=2022-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220519205358/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/28/us/baltimore-freddie-gray.html}}</ref>。截至2015年4月30日，全国范围内有22场示威直接回应格雷的死亡，或声援巴尔的摩<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.elephrame.com/textbook/protests|title=At least 857 Black Lives Matter demonstrations have been held in the last 286 days|website=Elephrame|publisher=Elephrame|accessdate=2015-04-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141226205743/https://www.elephrame.com/textbook/protests|archivedate=2014-12-26}}</ref>。

2015年4月18日，数百人参与了在巴尔的摩警察局门外的抗议<ref>{{cite news|last1=Fenton|first1=Justin|title=Hundreds at Baltimore police station protest over man's injuries during arrest|url=http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/maryland/bs-md-shooting-20150418-story.html|accessdate=2015-04-30|publisher=The Baltimore Sun|date=2015-04-18|archive-date=2015-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150505095655/http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/maryland/bs-md-shooting-20150418-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年4月21日，据[[路透社|路透社]]报道，“数百名示威者聚集在巴尔的摩”，和平抗议格雷的死亡<ref name=":2">{{Cite news|title = Crowds protest death of man after arrest by Baltimore police|url = http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/04/21/us-usa-police-baltimore-idUSKBN0NC1MC20150421|newspaper = Reuters|date = 2015-04-21|access-date = 2015-04-22|last = Simpson|first = Ian|archive-date = 2015-04-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150424035348/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/04/21/us-usa-police-baltimore-idUSKBN0NC1MC20150421|dead-url = no}}</ref>。次日，美国警察同业会（{{lang|en|Fraternal Order of Police}}）地区主席吉恩·瑞恩（{{lang|en|Gene Ryan}}）向格雷的家人表达同情，但批评“示威指桑骂槐”，认为“电视上的画面和声音很像是暴民传出的。”格雷家的律师威廉·墨菲（{{lang|en|William Murphy}}）要求吉恩“立即道歉并收回言论<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/maryland/baltimore-city/bs-md-ci-fop-news-conference-20150422-story.html|title=Baltimore police union president likens protests to 'lynch mob'|author=Baltimore Sun|date=2015-04-22|work=baltimoresun.com|accessdate=2015-04-28|archive-date=2019-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190212111718/https://www.baltimoresun.com/news/maryland/baltimore-city/bs-md-ci-fop-news-conference-20150422-story.html}}</ref>。”瑞恩在两天后为他的言论辩解，承认措辞很下流<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/04/24/union-protesters-lynch-mob_n_7138282.html|title=Police Union Chief Defends Calling Baltimore Protesters A 'Lynch Mob'|work=The Huffington Post|accessdate=2015-04-28|archive-date=2018-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180504141455/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/04/24/union-protesters-lynch-mob_n_7138282.html}}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》评论员查尔斯·布鲁（{{lang|en|Charles M.Blow}}）提到了他几年前写的一篇专栏，表示抗议比滥用私刑更为极端，因为抗议贬低了美国私刑的历史意义，挑起种族间的紧张关系<ref name="nyti_‘Lyn">{{Cite web| title = <nowiki>‘Lynch Mob’: Misuse of Language</nowiki>| last = Blow| first = Charles M.| work = The New York Times| date = 2015-04-27| accessdate = 2015-04-27| url = http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/27/opinion/charles-blow-lynch-mob-misuse-of-language.html| quote = <nowiki>“Lynch mob” is the same ghastly rhetorical overreach that is often bandied about in political discussions — including in this column I wrote seven years ago. It was a too-extreme comparison then, and it’s a too-extreme comparison now.</nowiki>| archive-date = 2021-07-06| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210706204346/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/27/opinion/charles-blow-lynch-mob-misuse-of-language.html}}</ref>。

2015年4月25日，巴尔的摩市中心爆发抗议活动，示威者投掷石块和纵火让示威升级为暴动<ref name=Stolberg>{{cite news|last1=Stolberg|first1=Sheryl Grey|title=National Guard Activated in Baltimore as Police and Youths Clash After Funeral for Freddie Gray|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/28/us/a-call-for-peace-before-freddie-grays-funeral-in-baltimore.html?hp&action=click&pgtype=Homepage&module=first-column-region&region=top-news&WT.nav=top-news&_r=0|accessdate=2015-04-28|publisher=New York Times|date=2015-04-28|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912060312/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/28/us/baltimore-freddie-gray.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。至少34人被捕，15名警察受伤<ref name=":8" /><ref name=":6">{{Cite web|title = Freddie Gray death: 12 arrested during protests - CNN.com|url = http://www.cnn.com/2015/04/25/us/baltimore-freddie-gray-protest/index.html|website = CNN|accessdate = April 25, 2015|date = April 25, 2015|last = Marquez|first = Miguel|last2 = Almasy|first2 = Steve|archive-date = 2015-04-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150427220446/http://www.cnn.com/2015/04/25/us/baltimore-freddie-gray-protest/index.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>Wenger, Yvonne; Campbell, Colin. [http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/maryland/baltimore-city/bs-md-ci-protest-arrests-20150426-story.html City leader calls for peace after 35 arrested, 6 officers injured] {{Wayback|url=http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/maryland/baltimore-city/bs-md-ci-protest-arrests-20150426-story.html |date=20150427211610 }}, Baltimore Sun, 2015-04-26.</ref>。4月27日格雷的葬礼结束后，出现骚乱和抢劫<ref name=wsj-funeral>{{cite web|title=Freddie Gray’s Funeral Draws Thousands in Baltimore|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/freddie-grays-funeral-draws-thousands-in-baltimore-1430147862|website=The Wall Street Journal|accessdate=2015-04-27|archive-date=2015-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150429050131/http://www.wsj.com/articles/freddie-grays-funeral-draws-thousands-in-baltimore-1430147862|dead-url=no}}</ref>，两名巡逻车被毁，15名警察据报受伤<ref name=":8">{{Cite news|title = Baltimore police, protesters clash; 15 officers hurt|url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2015/04/27/baltimore-credible-threat/26454875/|newspaper = USA Today|date = 2015-04-27|access-date = 2015-04-27|last = Bacon|first = John|archive-date = 2018-06-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180617193731/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2015/04/27/baltimore-credible-threat/26454875/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。示威者抢劫并烧毁了巴尔的摩市中心的一家CVS药店<ref name="cnn._Balt">{{Cite web|title = Baltimore protests turn violent; police injured - CNN.com|last = Ford|first = Dana|work = CNN.com|date = April 27, 2015|accessdate = April 27, 2015|url = http://www.cnn.com/2015/04/27/us/baltimore-unrest/index.html|language = |quote = |archive-date = 2018-02-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180212012316/https://www.cnn.com/2015/04/27/us/baltimore-unrest/index.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

为应对骚乱，马里兰州警方调遣82名警察保护城市<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.wbaltv.com/news/downtown-businesses-organizations-close-early-monday/32595778|title=Gov. declares state of emergency; activates National Guard|publisher=WBAL-TV|accessdate=2015-04-30|archive-date=2019-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190102001117/https://www.wbaltv.com/news/downtown-businesses-organizations-close-early-monday/32595778}}</ref>。原定举行的[[巴尔的摩金莺|巴尔的摩金莺]]队对阵[[芝加哥白袜|芝加哥白袜]]队的三連戰因骚乱，第一場不開放觀眾入場，為MLB史上首次關門比賽，後二場被推迟<ref name="bsun-postponed">{{cite news|title=Tonight's Orioles game postponed amid violence downtown|url=http://www.baltimoresun.com/sports/orioles/blog/bal-as-turmoil-currently-envelops-the-city-tonights-orioles-game-against-the-chicago-white-sox-is-stille-20150427-story.html|accessdate=2015-04-27|work=Baltimore Sun|archive-date=2016-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160207181259/http://www.baltimoresun.com/sports/orioles/blog/bal-as-turmoil-currently-envelops-the-city-tonights-orioles-game-against-the-chicago-white-sox-is-stille-20150427-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，且在之後約一個月期間，巴尔的摩金莺的主場賽事都在對手球場舉行。马里兰州州长拉里·霍根宣布进入紧急状态，出动国民警卫队<ref name="emergencystate">{{Cite news|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/hundreds-people-clash-police-baltimore-mall/story?id=30622868|title=Maryland Gov. Declares State of Emergency After Violent Clashes in Baltimore|first=Emily|last=Shapiro|date=2015-04-27|accessdate=2015-04-27|work=ABC News|archive-date=2015-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428063223/http://abcnews.go.com/US/hundreds-people-clash-police-baltimore-mall/story?id=30622868|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=maryland-emergencystate>{{cite web|title=Governor Larry Hogan Signs Executive Order Declaring State Of Emergency, Activating National Guard|url=https://governor.maryland.gov/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/EO-4-27-2015.pdf|publisher=Government of Maryland|accessdate=2015-04-27|archive-date=2019-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427045729/https://governor.maryland.gov/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/EO-4-27-2015.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。霍根还要求巴尔的摩500名当班，并从其他州份另外抽调5000名警察<ref>{{Cite tweet |user= matthewhaybrown |number= 592853842485780481 |date=April 27, 2015 |title=Maryland State Police activating 500 officers for Baltimore; requesting up to 5,000 from neighboring states}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/maryland/baltimore-city/bal-university-of-baltimore-closes-amid-high-school-purge-threat-20150427-story.html|title=Riots erupt across West Baltimore, downtown|work=The Baltimore Sun|accessdate=2015-04-30|archive-date=2019-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502054433/https://www.baltimoresun.com/news/maryland/baltimore-city/bal-university-of-baltimore-closes-amid-high-school-purge-threat-20150427-story.html}}</ref>。

