nesses-organizations-close-early-monday/32595778| language = | quote = | archive-date = 2019-01-02| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190102001117/https://www.wbaltv.com/news/downtown-businesses-organizations-close-early-monday/32595778}}</ref><ref name="lati_Balt"/><ref name="amer_Viol"/>，学校旅行被取消至五月中旬<ref name="balt_Balt"/><ref name="abc2_Conc">{{Cite web|title=Concerns over violence leads to area closings in Baltimore |last=Staff |first=WMAR |work=WMAR |publisher=The E.W. Scripps Company |date= |accessdate=2015-04-27 |url=http://www.abc2news.com/news/region/baltimore-city/university-of-maryland-baltimore-closing-early |quote= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150430150259/http://www.abc2news.com/news/region/baltimore-city/university-of-maryland-baltimore-closing-early |archivedate=2015-04-30 }}</ref>，4月28日关闭全市学校<ref name="usat_Balt">{{Cite web| title = Baltimore police, protesters clash; 15 officers hurt| last = Bacon| first = John| last2 = Welch| first2 = William M.| work = USA Today| publisher = Gannett Company| date = 2015-04-27| accessdate = 2015-04-27| url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2015/04/27/baltimore-credible-threat/26454875/| quote = Police said more than two dozen people were arrested. The city's schools were canceled for Tuesday.| archive-date = 2018-06-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180617193731/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2015/04/27/baltimore-credible-threat/26454875/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。此外，市中心的马里兰州大学校区和Mondawmin超市提前关闭<ref name="nyti_Nati">{{Cite web| title = National Guard Called Out in Baltimore as Police and Youths Clash After Funeral for Freddie Gray| last = Stolberg| first = Sheryl Gay| work = The New York Times| date = 2015-04-27| accessdate = 2015-04-27| url = http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/28/us/a-call-for-peace-before-freddie-grays-funeral-in-baltimore.html?_r=0| quote = | archive-date = 2015-04-27| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150427220927/http: